name: The Last Pepe
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
We all know that the world of memes can be a battlefield, with different factions fighting for dominance. But amidst the chaos, one Pepe has stood the test of time and emerged as the last frog standing – Froggo, the Last Pepe!

$FROGGO is a meme coin with no intrinsic value or expectation of financial return. There is no formal roadmap. The coin is completely for entertainment purposes only.

NO TAX, 0% Buy & Sell tax, contract renounced..

Stake your FROGGO tokens to earn  more. 105% annually.
